官　黃憶筑\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　7 　　月　　28　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e6%af%92%e8%81%b2%2c615%2c20220728%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,毒聲,615,20220728,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"毒聲","JNO":"615","JDATE":"20220728","JTITLE":"聲請觀察勒戒"}